{"tid":514093,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"到先達求換機遭打腫眼 鄰國漢：唔再嚟香港買手機","createTime":"2017-12-30T08:10:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-30T11:08:59.000Z","uid":136994,"like":266,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":55,"replies":[{"pid":"d2b48723476f63e02368d7d47fab081da8423231","tid":514093,"uid":136994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T08:10:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20171230/57644156?_ga=2.252478985.1684942651.1514468360-575505850.1502150827\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171230%2F57644156%3F_ga%3D2.252478985.1684942651.1514468360-575505850.1502150827&d=tq1kDz1fn1a4gO7PTbgixGi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=94dadc78\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171230%2F57644156%3F_ga%3D2.252478985.1684942651.1514468360-575505850.1502150827&h=796a788c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20171230/57644156?_ga=2.252478985.1684942651.1514468360-575505850.1502150827</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171230/large/1514615732_7029.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171230%2Flarge%2F1514615732_7029.jpg&h=99f37c93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n旺角先達發生內地客換手機不果遭打傷事件。一名39歲持雙程證姓魏男子，早前來港在旺角亞皆老街先達廣場一店舖，購得一部iPhone 6S給女兒，惟不久疑因手機電池發脹，出現屏幕爆裂，懷疑購得的手機是贋品，遂於今日早上11時許，攜同手機返回店舖理論，要求換手機。<br />\n<br />\n現場消息指，當時店東堅稱手機是真貨，不予退換，魏見換機不果，一度情緒激動。其間一名年約30歲男子，疑不滿被其聲浪滋擾，一度搶去魏的手機揮舞，並扑打事主。魏右眼角及手部受傷，需送院治理，涉案男子則逃去無蹤。<br />\n<br />\n魏在醫院候診期間，向在場記者展示其傷勢，可見他右眼瘀腫，眼角有一道傷口。精神萎頓的他揚言，以後不會再來香港購買手機，「唔會啦！呃人的，會返內地買。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢啲算唔算一物治一物<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9185a72c0f421491a0baef6f5463c4da2c08c11e","tid":514093,"uid":85819,"like":42,"dislike":2,"sco